Implement all helpers before build().

── SHARED (both modes) ──────────────────

section_header(title)
  Returns a full-width Table with BRAND_DARK background and white 11pt bold text.
  Padding: top/bottom=6, left/right=8. No grid lines.

side_by_side(img1, caption1, img2, caption2, h=2.5*inch)
  Returns a 2-column Table. Each cell: Image (width=W/2 - 0.1in, height=h)
  followed by caption in caption_style. Missing file → caption only. No borders.

img_full(filename, caption_text, h=3.5*inch)
  Returns a centered full-width image with caption in caption_style below it.

── COMPETITIVE mode only ─────────────────

callout(text, label="UNLIKE NEWSELA")
  Amber box with a colored left accent bar (0.12in wide).
  - "UNLIKE NEWSELA:" prefix → red bar (#C0392B), label starts with "▌"
  - "UNIQUE TO [PRODUCT]:" prefix → BRAND_ACCENT bar, label starts with "★"
  - Label: 8pt bold BRAND_ACCENT on AMBER (verify 4.5:1)
  - Body: 8.5pt DKGRAY on AMBER
  - Wrap in KeepTogether([Spacer(1,6), callout, Spacer(1,6)])

── NEWSELA_OVERVIEW mode only ────────────

callout(text, label="LUNA")
  Colored box with no left bar. Three label types:
  - "LUNA"    → LUNA_PURPLE text on light purple bg (#EDE9FE), prefix "★ LUNA AI · "
  - "KEY"     → DARK_TEAL text on light teal bg (#E0F2FE), prefix "◆ KEY INSIGHT · "
  - default   → ACCENT_GREEN text on light green bg (#D1FAE5), prefix "✓ NOTE · "
  - Font: Helvetica-Bold 10.5pt, leading=16, borderPad=8, leftIndent=10, rightIndent=10
  - Wrap in KeepTogether([Spacer(1,6), callout, Spacer(1,6)])

