  • Padding: top/bottom=4–5, left/right=6–7
  • VALIGN TOP on all cells
  • Snapshot table col 0: BRAND_DARK background every row, snap_label_style text
    Set this at the Paragraph level — TableStyle TEXTCOLOR alone will NOT work

